            <h3>Typical Repair Costs</h3>
            <p>Our pricing includes everything that ensures a high-quality repair:</p>

            <ul class="space-y-4">
                <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-[#ca0913] flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-1">Flat-rate diagnostic fee (credited toward repair)</li>
                <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-[#ca0913] flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-1">Genuine Whirlpool OEM parts</li>
                <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-[#ca0913] flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-1">Factory-trained technician labor</li>
                <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-[#ca0913] flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-1">Insurance, office support, and EPA compliance</li>
                <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-[#ca0913] flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-1"><strong>90-day warranty on all repairs</strong></li>
              </ul>
          </div>
          <p style="margin-top: 20px;">For average washer repair pricing, visit our <a href="/price-list/washer-repair-cost/" class="underline font-bold" style="color: #dc2626 !important;">Washer Repair Cost Guide</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="page-container" id="anchor-6">
        <div class="header-container">
          <div class="head-content-h">
